---
title: One-Pan Cheeseburger Lettuce Wraps with Crispy Fried Onions, Pickles & Special Sauce
description: How do you make a cheeseburger more fun? Skip the bun! These lettuce wraps feature all the classic burger fixin’s you love, stuffed inside romaine for a crunchy twist. First, ground beef is cooked with melty cheddar, then the filling is nestled into lettuce leaves and topped with crispy fried onions, chopped pickles, and special sauce. Yep, this lettuce wrap is one of those things you’ll have to see to be-leaf!
